data.name: textBox25.Value
data.value: A student is not considered accepted and will not be admitted to class until arrangements to pay full tution fees have been completed. After the approval of student visa by Canadian Authority, no refund will be made if an applicant does not come to Canada for personal reason. We look forward to having you as a student of Cornerstone Academic College. If you need any further assistance, please feel free to contact us.
